#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 紫气东来
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_1_NAME"
msgstr "Tử Khí Đông Lai"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 天地灵气充沛，修士修行速度大增，修行欲望...
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_1_DESC"
msgstr "Thiên Tượng Nhất: Mô Tả"
"Heavenly spiritual qi is abundant, cultivators' cultivation speed greatly "
"increases, and the desire to cultivate improves"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 金煞之年
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_2_NAME"
msgstr "Kim Sát Chi Niên"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 金煞充盈天地肃杀，修士更大可能嗜血而相互...
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_2_DESC"
msgstr "Thiên Tượng Nhị: Mô Tả"
"Golden malice fills the world with solemnity, cultivators are more likely to"
" be bloodthirsty and attack each other"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 木灵盛世
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_3_NAME"
msgstr "Mộc Linh Chi Thế"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 木德滋养生机盎然，采集收获倍增且伤势恢复...
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_3_DESC"
msgstr "Thiên Tượng Tam: Mô Tả"
"Wood virtue nourishes with vitality, harvesting yields double and injuries "
"heal extremely fast, ideal for searching for heavenly materials and earthly "
"treasures everywhere"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 水德之纪
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_4_NAME"
msgstr "Thủy Đức Kỷ Nguyên"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 水行流转通达无碍，修炼效率与速度双重提升...
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_4_DESC"
msgstr "Thiên Tượng Tứ: Mô Tả"
"Water element flows without hindrance, cultivation efficiency and speed both"
" improve, making it a great time for secluded cultivation"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 火劫时代
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_5_NAME"
msgstr "Hỏa Kiếp Chi Thế"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 天火燃烧劫数降临，战力暴涨但寿元流逝，当...
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_5_DESC"
