"Five elements are out of order and heaven and earth are in chaos, "
"conventional cultivation yields half the result with twice the effort, but "
"bottlenecks loosen and it is suitable to attempt breakthroughs"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 天道均衡
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_8_NAME"
msgstr "Thiên Đạo Cân Bằng"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 天道显化损有余而补不足，高阶修士进境受阻...
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_8_DESC"
msgstr "Thiên Tượng Bát: Mô Tả"
"Heavenly Dao manifests to take from those who have too much and give to "
"those who have too little, high-level cultivators' progress is hindered, "
"low-level cultivators should seize the opportunity to catch up"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 劫数将至
msgid "CELESTIAL_PHENOMENON_9_NAME"
msgstr "Đại Kiếp Lâm Đầu"

#. celestial_phenomenon.csv: 劫数降临戾气弥漫，虽战力激增但福缘浅薄，...
